snippet.title: SpellForce 3: Soul Harvest Campaign Part 16 - The Jade Staff Ritual, Amber Lake & the Leonidar Gorge
snippet.description:
Pretty cool little battle early on, wish it was longer but finally we can get some Titans in battle, the vengeful spirit sidequest is finished, unfortunately a bit longer video than I hoped for but we got alot of side quests going.

Leave a like, comment and subscribe to show your support, and thank you!

In case you want more lore than my rambling can provide, check out Wormic's vids: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCeqOnqkcoKozWe_-X15rLiw
Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/817540/SpellForce_3_Soul_Harvest/
GOG: https://www.gog.com/game/spellforce_3_soul_harvest
SpellForce Discord: https://discord.com/invite/spellforce
